metadata.name: JOY OF PAIN
metadata.description:
The influences sometimes hurt. But with every punch in the face you feel the energy that the pain awakens in you.

Driven by the beats and vibes you make the right moves.

This is how the pain makes you happy and acts like a drug that you can't get rid of.

AI generated artwork - manually enhanced.

4,096 x 4,096 pix - 72 dpi

December 2022
